		## â€” Ii sأ،hte luohttit Suoma beale Ohcejoga fuoؤ‘ؤ‘o- ja guolledoalu dutkanguovddأ،إ¾a interneahtta siidduid gأ،vdnojit statistihkkat Deanu sأ،laإ،meriid birra.
		#maybe not strict enough

SETCHILD (V <TH-Inf>)  TO (1 @>N OR @>A OR @<SUBJ OR @SUBJ> OR Pcle LINK 1 @<OBJ OR @OBJ> LINK *1 Inf BARRIER (*) - Adv - @ADVL - Pcle);
