SETCHILD <LO-Loc-Plc> OR <LO-Loc-Any> (NEGATE c آ§ANYROLE) TO (*1 Sem/Place + Loc OR Loc + Sem/Furn OR Loc + Sem/Build OR Loc + Sem/Org OR Loc + Sem/Veh OR Adv + Sem/Plc BARRIER NPNHA - @<ADVL - @>P);
