(NEGATE *1 (V Pl3) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(NEGATE *-1 (V Pl3) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR VFIN)(NEGATE -1 (Pcle Qst) LINK -1 (V Pl3));
