	#$ Mii leat hui giitevaؤچؤچat go ON-a Earenoamأ،إ،dieؤ‘iheaddjis ledje ؤچielga أ،vإ¾إ¾uhusat davviriikkaid rأ،ؤ‘ؤ‘ehusaide, ja go muittuhii midjiide ahte davviriikat berrejit leat bأ،lggesؤچuovgit eamiأ،lbmogiid vuoigatvuoؤ‘aid ektui, dadjأ، Lأ،ila Susanne Vars.
	## Earأ، jearaldagaid sأ،htأ،t jearret kunddarguovddأ،إ¾is, telefuvdna 06640.
