ADD:real-ImprtDu1-DerPassPrsSg3 (&real-ImprtDu1-DerPassPrsSg3) TARGET (N Sg Nom Err/Confused-DerPassPrsSg3) OR (V TV Imprt Du1) OR (Ind Prs Sg3 Err/Confused) IF (NEGATE *1 ("!"))(-1 Ess LINK -1 BOS)(NEGATE -1 (A Attr) OR (A Sg Nom)  OR (N Gen) - Sem/Time - Sem/Place OR VFIN OR Inf OR Dem)(*1 THAT-CS BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(NEGATE 0 Der/Pass - Err/Confused-Any)(NEGATE 0 (Prs Sg3));

