(NEGATE -1 ConNeg LINK -1 Neg LINK -1 Loc)
(NEGATE 1 PrfPrc)(NEGATE 0 <AG-Nom-Ani> LINK *-1 BE + Ind OR BE + Cond OR BE + (Pot) OR CAN + Ind OR CAN + Cond OR NOT-V + Ind BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - (Pers Nom) - (Adv Sem/Time) - (Adv Sem/Plc) - @OBJ> - @ADVL - (N Loc) - (N Ill) - (N Sg Acc PxSg3) - (N Sg Gen PxSg3) LINK NOT *-1 SUBJ + Sem/Animate OR SUBJ + Sem/Org OR CS BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)
(NEGATE 0 (A Ess) + Sem/Hum LINK *-1 BE + Sg3)
(NEGATE 0 (A Ess) LINK -1 GRADE-ADV)
