	## Njulge kأ،rta dakkأ،r sadjأ،i gokko lea jalgat Bonja kأ،rtta nu ahte davvi guovlu kأ،rttas ja kompأ،ssa davvi guovlu heiveba oktii Bija kompأ،ssaduolbba ravdda nu ahte mannأ، dan bأ،ikkis gos leat dأ،l, dohkko gosa أ،iggut Bonja kompأ،ssajorbbأ، nu ahte sأ،zut jorbbأ،s إ،addet dأ،ssأ،laga davvisأ،zuiguin kأ،rttas Heivet kompأ،ssa davvinjuola, gأ،hta sisa Mannannjuolla ؤچأ،jeha gosa galggat mannat
	
ADD:xreal-dohkko-dohko (&real-dohkko-dohko) TARGET ("doahkkut" V IV Ind Prt Pl3) OR ("doahkkut" Ex/V Ex/IV Der/PassS V IV Ind Prs Sg3) OR ("doahkkut" Ex/V Ex/IV Der/PassS V IV Ind Prs ConNeg) OR ("doahkkut" V IV Imprt ConNegII) OR ("doahkkut" V IV ConNegII) OR ("doahkkut" V IV Ind Prs Du1) OR ("dohko" Err/Orth Adv) IF (*0 <TH-Ill-Any> OR <LO-Ill-Any> OR <DE-Ill-*Ani> OR <DE-Ill-Plc> OR <TH-Nom-Any><PO-Ill-Any> OR <TH-Acc-Any><DE-Ill-*Ani> BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY) ;
