	# fitnat (visit) vs. fidnet (get)
	# -------------------------------
ADD:fidnet (&real-fidnet) TARGET ("fitnat" V IV Ind Prs Pl3) OR ("fitnat" V IV Ind Prt Sg2) OR ("fitnat" V IV Imprt Pl2) OR ("fitnet" N Sg Nom) IF (*1 Acc OR Gen BARRIER NPNHA LINK NEGATE *1 N OR A BARRIER NPNH)(NEGATE *-1 (Imprt Pl2)) ;

