COPY:real-fidnet ("fidnet" V TV Inf SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("fitnat" V IV Ind Prs Pl3 &real-fidnet) OR ("fitnat" V IV Ind Prt Sg2 &real-fidnet) OR ("fitnat" V IV Imprt Pl2 &real-fidnet) OR ("fitnet" N Sg Nom &real-fidnet) TARGET (&real-fidnet) ;
