COPY:&real-muhtumin ("muhtumin" Adv SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("muhtumin" Err/Orth Adv &real-muhtumin) OR ("muohttit" Ex/V Ex/IV Der/PassS V &real-muhtumin) OR ("muhttot" V IV Actio Ess &real-muhtumin) OR ("muhttit" Ex/V Ex/TV Der/PassS V IV Actio Ess &real-muhtumin) OR ("muhttot" Ex/V Ex/IV Der/NomAct N Ess &real-muhtumin) OR ("muhttot" Ex/V Ex/IV Der/NomAct Sem/Act N Ess &real-muhtumin) OR ("muhttit" Ex/V Ex/TV Der/PassS Ex/V Ex/IV Der/NomAct N Ess &real-muhtumin) OR ("muohttit" Ex/V Ex/IV Der/PassS Ex/V Ex/IV Der/NomAct N Ess &real-muhtumin) TARGET (&real-muhtumin) ;
