	#$ Doloإ، vallji dealljأ، ja ؤچeavrأ، bivddus Oarje-Finnmأ،rkku sulluin ledje duإ،إ،e bأ،zahusat vel bأ،hcأ،n. 
	#$ Eai sii oro oaidnime mأ،id boraspirevallji dagaha ealأ،husaide, eaige oainne mأ،id boraspirevallji dagaha boraspiriide maid, oaivvilda NBR joؤ‘iheaddji Niillas Heandarat Sara, iige أ،iggo muitalit mأ،id NBR stivra lea evttohan riikaؤچoahkkimii dأ،n أ،إ،إ،is.
	#$ Dأ،lkkأ،datrievdama geaإ¾il liegga mearra ja mielddisbuktأ، mearehis olu dorskevallji Barentsأ،bis.
	#$ Albmأ،i bأ،htara rastأ، jأ،vrri أ،ibbas أ،lأ،s ja su oaguhit olmmoإ،vallji sأ،ittiin. --- a crowd of people  oaguhit su with sأ،ittiin
	#$ Kulturbirrasiid vallji Davvin



    # valljugas vs. (valjis) vallji
    # ---------------------------------
    # condition:
 
   
ADD:xlex-valjis-valljugas (&lex-valjis-valljugas) TARGET ("vallji") IF (0 PxSg3 OR (A Sg Loc)) (*1 NP-HEAD BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHCCA)(NEGATE 1 Sem/Ani OR Sem/Hum LINK NEGATE 0 Gen LINK *1 NP-HEAD BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHCCA) ;

COPY:lex-valjis-valljugas ("valljugas" A Sg Nom SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("vallji" N Sg Loc &lex-valjis-valljugas) OR ("vallji" A Sg Loc &lex-valjis-valljugas) OR ("vallji" N Sg Gen PxSg3 &lex-valjis-valljugas) OR ("vallji" N Sg Acc PxSg3 &lex-valjis-valljugas) OR ("valjis" Adv &lex-valjis-valljugas) TARGET (&lex-valjis-valljugas) ;
