ADD:real-varra (&real-varra) TARGET ("vأ،rra" Adv) OR ("vأ،rra" N Sem/State Sg Nom) IF (*-1 ConNeg + VARRA-SUBJ-V BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE LINK *-1 (Neg Ind Sg3) + <aux> BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(NEGATE -1 VأپRRA-CMP-FIRST) ;
