COPY:lex-guorralit-guorrasit ("guorrasit" IV SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("guorrat" Ex/V TV Der/l &lex-guorralit-guorrasit) AFTER V TARGET (&lex-guorralit-guorrasit) ;
