ADD:xlex-badjel-rastأ، (&lex-badjel-rastأ،) TARGET ("badjel") IF (*0 MOVEMENT-V - ("girdit") BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY)(-1 RASTA-PLACE) (NEGATE 1 Num OR Sem/Measr OR Sem/Curr); 
