ADD:xmsyn-gii-mii (&msyn-gii-mii) TARGET WHO (*-1 N - Coll - ("Sأ،pmi") - ("sأ،pmi") - ("suohkan") BARRIER (*) - COMMA LINK 0 Sem/Group OR GROUP-WORDS LINK NEGATE 0 Loc LINK *-1 Sem/Hum + Nom OR Acc BARRIER NPNH) ; #CHECK tag change
