ADD:xmsyn-Sg3-ConNeg (&msyn-Sg3-ConNeg) TARGET (V Prs Sg3) IF (0 Ind OR Cond)(-1 (V Neg Sg3) LINK NOT 0 Sup LINK NEGATE 1 COMMA OR (".*ge"r))(NEGATE 0 ConNeg)(NEGATE -1 COMMA OR Rel);	#CHECK change tag to &msyn-Sg3-ConNeg
