	## Amma Anne G ii suhttأ، munnje, jus in ؤچأ،le nu ؤچأ،bbأ،t go أ،iggoإ،ii?
	## Dat ii leat rأ،ؤ‘ؤ‘ehusa vuollأ،saإ، orgأ،na, ja rأ،ؤ‘ؤ‘ehusas ii lea danne ovddasvأ،stأ،dus Sأ،medikki politihkalaإ، doaimmas dahje dain politihkalaإ، mearrأ،dusain maid Sأ،mediggi dahkأ،.
	## Omd. go vuodjit biilla ( dahje skohtera dahje njealljejuvlaga ) mis ii galgأ، leat badjel 0,2 promille alkohola varas. 
	## Don fertet duإ،إ،e dohkkehit ahte ii dأ،hpأ،huvvأ، nu ollu juste dأ،l. 
	## Jus duإ،إ،e veardidivؤچؤچii sojahangehؤچosiid bokte, iige vأ،lddأ،إ،ii vuhtii stuorit
	## antesedeanta pro:ii, muhto antesedeanta ii adnoإ،ii , go pro almmatge birge dan haga.
	#$ ) ii ii ii (.
	## Jus bأ،rdni dupmehallet seksualalaإ، oktavuhttin ja veagalvأ،ldin, de sahtta son ؤچohkka giddagassii olles 15 jأ،gi, muhttu politi-inspektأ¸ra Are Meedbye lohkأ، ahte dat ii lea realistalaإ،, ja sus ii leat makkarge oaivvil man guhkka raإ‹ggaإ،tus sahtta إ،addet. 
COPY:msyn-Sg3-ConNeg (ConNeg SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Sg3 Err/Orth &msyn-Sg3-ConNeg) TARGET (&msyn-Sg3-ConNeg) IF (NOT 0 Neg) ;	

	
	# double inchoative أ،lgit + -goahtit
	# ----------------------------------
	# two ways of fixing
	# أ،lgen mun ballat
	# mun ballagohten
	# HOW TO DISPLAY BOTH WAYS?
	
ADD:xsyn-double-inchoative (&syn-double-inchoative) TARGET BEGIN IF (*1 (Ex/V TV Der/InchL) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR VFIN LINK NEGATE 1 ("d") OR ("dii") OR ("dmu") OR ("dbm") OR (Num Sg Loc));
	## Go leimme mihtidan nu mأ،إ‹ga rusttega ahte أ،lggiime ollet lohppi, أ،lgen mun ballagoahtit.
	#$ mon أ،lggأ،n boahtte vahku bargagoahtit d. 700 #CHECK D?
	
ADD:xsyn-double-inchoative (&syn-double-inchoative) TARGET (Ex/V TV Der/InchL) IF (*-1 &syn-double-inchoative BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY);
	
COPY:double-inchoative (SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Ex/V TV Der/InchL) TARGET (&syn-double-inchoative) IF (*-1 &syn-double-inchoative BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY) ;


ADDRELATION:double-inchoative ($2 RIGHT) (&syn-double-inchoative) TO (-1 (&syn-double-inchoative));


