    # congruence case/ number
    # -----------------------

    # where do we have f?
    # number: subject - verb
    # case: subject - subject predicate
    # number: modifier (city) head (human) === be careful with this type
    # relative pronouns and their antecedents
    # habitive and subject predicate

    # secure, simple and general rule
