ADD:syn-number_congruence-subj-verb (&syn-number_congruence-subj-verb) TARGET (V Ind Prs) - ConNeg - Du3 - Pl2 OR (V Ind Prt) - ConNeg - Du3 - Pl2 OR (V Cond) - Du3 - Pl2 OR (V Neg Ind) - Du3 - Pl2 IF (-1 WHO + (Pl Nom) LINK NEGATE -1 (Pron Pers Pl1) OR (Pron Pers Pl2) OR (Pron Pers Du1) OR (Pron Pers Du2) OR (Pron Pers Du3))(NEGATE 0 (V Pl3) OR Pl3-INF-V + Sg2 OR Pl3-INF-V + Inf OR Pl3-INF-V + Pl1 - ("<.*at>r")  OR BE + (Prs Pl1) OR &real OR (Nآ Sg))(NEGATE 0 Du3 LINK *0 (Pron Du3) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(NEGATE 0 Du3 LINK *1 Sem/Human BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE LINK 1 CC LINK 1 Sem/Human)(NEGATE 0 PrfPrc OR Adv)(NEGATE 0 NUMCONGR-EXCEPT)(NEGATE 0 Du2 OR Pl2 LINK *-1 (Imprt Du2) OR (Imprt Pl2))
