ADD:xmsyn-plcom-plloc  (&msyn-plcom-plloc) TARGET (Pl Com) IF (0 NP-HEAD LINK *-1 CC OR COMMA BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA LINK -1 (&msyn-plcom-plloc) OR (Pl Loc) LINK *-1 OASSI OR (Num Sg Nom) OR (Num Sg Acc) OR LOC_BIRRA OR ("ollu") BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA)(NEGATE -1 Num) ;
