ADD:xmsyn-gen-nom (&msyn-gen-nom) TARGET DOUBLE-CONSONANT-NOUNS IF (0 (N Sg Gen) OR (N Sg Acc) LINK 0 Sem/Hum OR Sem/Org) (1 Sg3 + V)(-1 CS)(NEGATE *1 (N Sg Nom)) ;	 #2nd
