    # أپisttonmearkkat
    # ----------------

# General rule to select Err/Orth readings of quotation marks.
# The Err/Orth reading is coming from the morphological analysis.
# The idea is that we can easily correct things coming from the lexcicon,
# without further work.
# Outcommented for now, until we have decided which approach to take
# (this one, or the one below, with multiple, targeted cg rules).
